title: Volcanic Landscape
description: A view of a volcanic landscape featuring a prominent reddish volcanic cone surrounded by dark, rocky terrain. The sky is overcast with clouds, creating a moody atmosphere. In the background, additional volcanic formations can be seen, adding depth to the scene.

title: Aerial View of Coastal Landscape
description: An aerial photograph showcasing a coastal landscape with a mix of land and water. The image features a river flowing into the sea, surrounded by patches of farmland and wetlands. The colors range from vibrant greens and browns of the fields to the deep blue of the ocean, creating a striking contrast.

title: Granite Rock Formation
description: A large, smooth granite rock formation under a clear blue sky. The rock has a slightly curved shape and features some vertical lines and textures on its surface. In the foreground, there are patches of greenery and smaller rocks.

title: Geological Cross-Section
description: An illustration depicting a geological cross-section of a landscape. The image shows mountains with green vegetation on the surface, transitioning into a body of water. Below the surface, various geological layers are visible, indicating different rock formations and structures, including faults and sedimentary layers.

title: Rock Formations in a Natural Landscape
description: A stunning view of unique rock formations in a natural landscape, featuring towering cliffs and scattered boulders. The scene is set against a cloudy sky, with patches of green vegetation visible among the rocks, creating a contrast between the rugged terrain and the lush surroundings.

title: Mushroom Rock Formation
description: A striking rock formation resembling a mushroom, set against a bright blue sky with wispy clouds. The rock is predominantly white, with a wide cap and a slender stem, surrounded by a barren landscape.
